Package: dltam
Title: Dynamic Local Trend Association Measure (DLTAM)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Adam", "Shen", , "adamshen1@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of the dynamic local trend association measure
    (DLTAM) for time series, proposed by García-López, F. J., Batyrshin,
    I., and Gelbukh, A., in the paper "Dynamic Local Trend Associations in
    Analysis of Comovements of Financial Time Series"
    <doi:10.1007/978-3-319-67137-6_20>.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://adamoshen.github.io/dltam, https://github.com/adamoshen/dltam
